  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium heat.",
    "Thread hazelnuts, cheddar cheese, and a pinch of flour onto skewers, leaving a bit of space between each piece.",
    "Brush with lemon juice and season with salt, pepper, paprika, and garlic powder.",
    "Grill for 5-7 minutes or until cheese is melted and hazelnuts are toasted.",
    "Meanwhile, heat vegetable oil in a small skillet and brush the skewers with it for extra crispiness, if desired.",
    "If using smoked paprika, sprinkle it over the skewers before serving.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional cheddar cheese and lemon wedges, if desired."
